# Git and PRs

- Commit only when the user asks
- Include preview URL: `https://{branch}--aem-portfolio--devistic-asim.aem.page/`
- Run `npm run lint` before merge
- Do not commit secrets or `node_modules`
- PR template lives in `.github/pull_request_template.md`
- Use `gh` for GitHub operations

